This project is write in Mean stack technology (MongoDB,express,angular,nodejs)

To activate this project please do the following Or install MongoDB and run the batch file :

install MongoDB
Create DB with name Shauli
Create collections :
1. Posts
2 Comments
3.Users
4.Locations

In collections Users and Locations you need to insert values manually for example :

Locations :
{"Description" : "Tel Aviv Fans", "Latitude" : 32.06363, "Longitude" : 34.77623, "Name" : "Fans Club Tel Aviv" }
{"Description" : "In the city center", "Latitude" : 31.77723, "Longitude" : 35.22644, "Name" : "Fans Club Jerusalem" }
{"Description" : "Industrial Area", "Latitude" : 31.99095, "Longitude" : 34.77131, "Name" : "Fans Club reshon letzion" }

Users :
{"Username" : "refael", "Password" : 123456, "Firstname" : "refael", "Lastname" : "yehuda", "Gender" : "male", "Birthdate" : "29/9/89", "Seniority" : 1, "lastModified" : ISODate("2015-12-27T23:22:23.941Z"), "Role" : "admin" }
{"Username" : "yakir", "Password" : 123456, "Firstname" : "yakir", "Lastname" : "twito", "Gender" : "male", "Birthdate" : "14/3/89", "Seniority" : 3 }
{"Username" : "Dhay", "Password" : 123456, "Firstname" : "Dhay", "Lastname" : "yehuda", "Gender" : "male", "Birthdate" : ISODate("1971-09-29T00:00:00Z"), "Seniority" : 2, "Role" : "admin" }

After this changes the project will work with al features

